Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}堅強的內心充滿推理的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}永遠以最敏銳的節奏揭開案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.90,0:00:24.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}終於要公開帽子下的內容了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}目暮警官很酷的過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.40,0:00:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}看上去是小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}他的名字就是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.40,0:01:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被園子一起叫去商場買東西的我們幾個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.30,0:01:53.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但叔叔卻意外的捲入目暮警官的調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:58.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官他們正在調查婦女連續被毆打的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.10,0:02:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就在這時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.20,0:02:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}蘭在商場的停車場內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:04.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}發現了第四個受害者的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.30,0:02:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目暮警官等人繼續調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}但目暮警官的樣子卻有點不對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 請你再讓我們在這裡檢查一會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}應該還可以找到什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}而且我感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}犯人現在應該還在這附近才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.60,0:02:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那就隨便你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目暮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.70,0:02:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你該不會是還在意當年的那件案子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.10,0:02:50.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}藏在你那頂帽子下被封印了的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:57.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被封印的目暮的秘密(後編)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.40,0:03:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}車鑰匙借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.10,0:03:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}我看還得在這裏待上一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}想把東西放到車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}先到百貨公司去上一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}那你動作得快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.50,0:03:27.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}百貨公司應該快要關門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}那你順便幫我放吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.80,0:03:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}找到了 就是這輛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.40,0:03:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}旁邊這輛車是怎麼停的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}停的靠我們這麼近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.80,0:03:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}車門根本就打不開了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 我已經去確認過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.60,0:04:03.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}沒錯 第二位受害者也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}從自己開的車下來之後才到公園上廁所的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.80,0:04:12.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}但我還是不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}歹徒為何針對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}自己開車又打扮新潮的女孩子下手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}難道說這其中另有什麼原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:22.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}她們四人還有什麼共同點是我們沒發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.80,0:04:25.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}這裡也在清理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}要清理不會等關了門之後再清理嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}下一個洗手間要走到八樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼我連上廁所都這麼不順利啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.70,0:04:41.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天非常感謝各位顧客光臨本百貨公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}馬上就到了本館關門的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}歡迎各位有機會再次光臨本館購物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}不會吧 要關門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}我們把屍體搬走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.20,0:04:51.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她的鞋子掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.90,0:05:02.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}這只鞋子怎麼穿不上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:11.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}你剛才不是說有什麼地方怪怪的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}該不會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}沒錯沒錯 就是這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}現在化了黑人妝的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}是不會穿成那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}這麼說來 難道歹徒會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.10,0:05:38.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.90,0:05:42.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}先別關燈 我還裡面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等等 沒有人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}厚底鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}在這個停車場裏被殺害的藍澤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.70,0:06:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}其實腳下穿的原本應該是一雙厚底鞋是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為現在會化黑人妝的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.80,0:06:08.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}一般來說是不會穿平底的普通鞋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是吧 蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}歹徒為什麼要刻意把被害人的鞋子換掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想 他一定是不想被人發現這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}因為他攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}全都是穿厚底鞋開車的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.90,0:06:27.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}現在想想其他三位小姐遭到攻擊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}臉上也的確都化了誇張的黑人妝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}這麼說 這三名受害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}在被攻擊的當時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}穿著厚底鞋的可能性應該也很高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.40,0:06:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}我記得由美曾經跟我說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}藍澤小姐一年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}在這個停車場引發的那場交通意外 最大的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:54.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}就是因為她腳上穿了一雙厚底鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.40,0:06:56.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}減低了刹車的敏感度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}所以才會引發那場悲劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}在那場車禍中喪生的少年早就離婚的父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.80,0:07:07.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當時非常堅定肇事是因為這個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}結果卻沒有得到法官的認同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.30,0:07:11.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}他的父母早就離婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.50,0:07:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}對 聽說主要原因是因為他酗酒才離婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.90,0:07:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我還記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}這名離婚的父親好象叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}這個人應該姓“定金”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}沒錯 就是姓定金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.10,0:07:30.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}等等 剛才那位警衛好像也姓定金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.70,0:07:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}難道說這件案子的歹徒就是那個警衛嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}高木老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}你立刻去查清楚一年前那場車禍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}你們現在立刻去查出定金警衛的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}不過 你怎麼會知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}其實這很簡單啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}因為這名歹徒攻擊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.60,0:07:57.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}全都是穿了厚底鞋自己開車的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這點從車子外面根本就看不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.90,0:08:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}而且遭到攻擊的又全是這家百貨公司的顧客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.60,0:08:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.30,0:08:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}我才會覺得一直在地下停車場裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.90,0:08:12.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}看顧客上下車的警衛最可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.60,0:08:13.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.50,0:08:17.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}那名歹徒的身高在150公分上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有兩名被害者都指稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.30,0:08:23.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}而那名警衛說他的身高是167公分 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔你又故意裝傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}那些遭到攻擊的姐姐這麼說只不過是想表達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.90,0:08:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}她們認為歹徒的身高跟自己差不多罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}既然她們在案發當時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.10,0:08:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}腳上都穿了一雙超過10公分的厚底鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就表示歹徒的身高最少應該再加上10公分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}叔叔根本就是在明知故問嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.90,0:08:44.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}我們是在那幾個女孩到總局偵訊的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}替她們量的身高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}當時因為她們是來錄口供的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.50,0:08:53.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}所以才沒有穿那麼誇張的厚底鞋來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.70,0:08:55.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.60,0:08:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}如果歹徒想報復藍澤小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}他就不用埋伏在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}可以直接到她家找她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}難道你忘了嗎 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}這名死者今年才20歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}一年前那場車禍發生的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}她應該還未成年才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}警方不會發表未成年嫌疑犯的住址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因此歹徒也只能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在自己兒子被撞的這個停車場耐心等候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}因為他相信這個女孩一定會再來這個百貨公司的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.90,0:09:28.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是她始終沒有出現 把他的耐性全磨光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才會轉而遷怒那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}穿了厚底鞋又自己開車來的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}接連的下手攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 我已經查明整個案件了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}那個警衛果然就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}一年前在車禍中喪生的那名少年的父親
