Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.20,0:09:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.00,0:09:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}我在停車場裡找到了他的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}但是都沒有看到他的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.20,0:09:59.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼了 蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}園子怎麼還沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}她說把東西放到車上後去一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:08.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把東西放到車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}我記得她穿的鞋子也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.60,0:10:18.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.10,0:10:20.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}現在 我還在百貨公司裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.80,0:10:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我再告訴你更誇張的 實在是太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.30,0:10:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}剛才 我在洗手間裏是多坐了一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}可是他們也用不著這麼快就關燈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.80,0:10:51.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼 你笑什麼 園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.30,0:10:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}我只是覺得有點不大對勁而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被看到了 被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}我的臉被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.90,0:11:31.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}園子 你說話啊
