Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:41.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}就認為她也是一個穿了厚底鞋自己開車的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.20,0:11:45.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}她剛才說她在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.10,0:11:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}她還在百貨公司裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}電話是不是被切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}電話還沒有被切斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我只是聽到遠方有機器微微作響的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}機器的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}請您選擇一個喜歡的外框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.20,0:12:01.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}擺好姿勢之後就可以按按鈕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是照大頭貼的機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}這家百貨公司有大頭貼機器嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}我記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}10樓的餐飲街旁邊的樓梯間裡有兩台
