Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.20,0:12:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我想園子一定是想從那裡的電梯坐到樓下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼高木去把百貨公司的照明打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.80,0:12:27.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}目暮與佐藤搭電梯從上往下搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其他人由下向上搜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}保護那名少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}一定要抓到這名歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}請大家讓一下路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.70,0:12:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}目暮警官還真是幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為這次太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.40,0:12:48.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}這一次的事情與他第一件辦的案子實在太像了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:54.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了 你女兒和那個戴眼鏡的小鬼跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.10,0:13:33.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}錯不了 這的確是園子的手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}餐飲街的客人都表示沒有看到他們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}園子應該是跑到百貨公司裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}高木 你們還沒找到人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你們都是一群惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.10,0:14:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你們都是裝出一副清純的模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:03.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯罪不眨眼的小惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.60,0:14:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是惡魔就沒有活下去的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}停電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}該死 偏偏挑在這個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.40,0:14:21.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}園子 園子你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}先安靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.20,0:14:31.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是什麼東西散落在地上的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}是沙子 白米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}不對 應該再大一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}會不會是鋪放在水族箱的小石頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.90,0:14:40.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}寵物專櫃在四樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}那她應該就在四樓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.40,0:15:10.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}其實我只是想給你點教訓罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.50,0:15:17.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但你看到了我的臉 就休想活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.10,0:15:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}真是怪了 寵物專櫃根本就沒有人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}這就怪了 根本就沒有破壞或是散落的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}難道說 剛才的那個聲音是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}怪就怪你不該看到我的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.00,0:16:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麼樣 這感覺好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我問你傷害了別人你的心裡好過了點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.40,0:16:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我知道你是想對開車技術不好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}用這根正義的鐵錘執行正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.90,0:16:22.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是很不幸的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}這孩子只是將東西放到車上而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}她根本高中都還沒畢業
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.60,0:16:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你的這種行為根本不是在伸張正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.70,0:16:34.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也不是為了你那死去的兒子報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}你只不過是遷怒罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.40,0:16:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這全是你獨斷獨行 玩弄人命於股掌之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.10,0:16:44.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毫無意義可言的發洩行為罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你到現在還不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.60,0:17:02.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實我只是想讓那個女孩向我道歉罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我要她改穿規矩的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}對我在天國的兒子道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.10,0:17:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}好告慰他的在天之靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.50,0:17:15.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我一開始真的只有這個念頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}園子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.20,0:17:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.70,0:17:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要緊沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}好可怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}警官 你怎麼知道是在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}這沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我只是自然的被引到這裡罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}使這些石子引我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.10,0:17:54.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}警官 你不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}放心 這沒有什麼大礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}只是過去的那個舊傷裂了口而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}是我沒處理好過去留下的一道舊傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.20,0:19:35.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}那是他過去的案子留下的舊傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.30,0:19:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對 目暮就是為了掩飾他頭上的那道疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才會走到哪裡都戴著那頂帽子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.10,0:19:48.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}可是 對刑警來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.10,0:19:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}在執勤的時候負傷就等於勳章一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}他根本就不需要藏起來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}那到疤已經有20年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:56.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}我記得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:20:00.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k60}那還是在目暮剛當上刑警的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你也應該聽過才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}就是連續開車撞高中女生逃逸的那件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:15.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}嫌疑犯行兇的動機是受到不良高中女生的恐嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他一般都會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.80,0:20:20.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}看準了這些高中女生落單的時候才開車追撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}做法非常卑劣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}當年在不良少女群體之間非常流行一種訂做制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.50,0:20:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}將褶裙可以拉長的穿法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}卻因此成了他的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.90,0:20:36.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}一開始他在撞了人之後就會逃逸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.10,0:20:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但幾次之後他只要不把被害者撞死就不會甘休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因此我們警方只有警告附近的高中女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.80,0:20:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}千萬別再穿那種裙子到外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}的確就沒有同樣的悲劇發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個時候 有個高中女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}表示她願意負責將歹徒引誘出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.80,0:21:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還說這麼做是為了替她死去的朋友報仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我們自然是加以阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}但是那名女孩對警方向來非常反感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}根本不顧我們的阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.70,0:21:08.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}在無奈之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}我們才特別派目暮保護那名學生的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.20,0:21:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是嫌疑犯卻想把她和目暮一起撞死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.00,0:21:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還好目暮記下了那輛車的車號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.90,0:21:36.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}終於將嫌疑犯逮捕到案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}但是代價卻太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目暮還好 只是頭上受了一處重傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那位高中女生的頭部與身體卻遭到猛烈撞擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.90,0:21:51.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在我們趕到的時候就看到她渾身是血倒在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.90,0:21:58.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麼 目暮警官他不脫那頂帽子就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說得沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.70,0:22:02.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}不管誰看到他頭上那麼大的疤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.40,0:22:05.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}一定會詢問他傷勢的由來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.40,0:22:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}就逼得他必須要重新回想起當年那件案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以目暮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}才會用那頂帽子遮住他的傷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.10,0:22:19.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}畢竟那道疤痕代表了一段痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.20,0:22:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以目暮警官才會那麼反對引誘歹徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.00,0:22:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因為他不希望再有人像那個女孩一樣犧牲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.50,0:22:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}拜託
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.60,0:22:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}她的頭部與身體雖然受了重傷沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.40,0:22:34.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}但她沒有死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.40,0:22:38.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她後來還成了目暮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.20,0:22:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}松本警政廳長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.50,0:22:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你一定是來醫院探病的對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.60,0:22:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你來得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.40,0:22:49.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}高木警官跟白鳥警官幾分鐘前才剛剛回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.50,0:22:52.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他們兩個也都來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.50,0:22:56.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 他們說畢竟是工作上的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.30,0:22:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她的額頭上有道疤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.80,0:23:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.90,0:23:02.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}小碧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.40,0:23:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}快來幫我削蘋果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.10,0:23:09.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}年紀這麼大了還是喜歡撒嬌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.30,0:23:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看來 我得快點讓他開始工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.00,0:23:13.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}他才會有點活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.20,0:23:16.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}是啊 到時候還要麻煩您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.50,0:23:19.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.20,0:23:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}聽說目暮警官的老婆小碧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}過去好像也曾經荒唐過一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這麼說來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.00,0:23:28.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}目暮警官之所以不把帽子脫掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.60,0:23:30.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}是因為他不希望別人看到之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}就取笑他與他老婆認識的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.10,0:23:39.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還沒有好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.30,0:23:48.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}由我和那傢伙來一起揭開21世紀的序幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.30,0:23:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}新一的推理和基德的魔術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.30,0:23:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}宿命對決的120分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.30,0:23:54.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}光輝的延續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.30,0:23:56.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}名偵探柯南2001特別節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.40,0:23:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}2001年1月8日週一晚放送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.70,0:24:02.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.10,0:24:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}10元硬幣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}下一回是2001年的2小時特別篇 是1月8日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.30,0:24:08.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}是1月8日 1月8日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.50,0:24:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是1月8日
